{"id":"b61b1b0a-3487-4774-bb44-fbb2cfc900ee","name":"Telemachus | Odyssey","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_e9341c11-9a54-48e0-b29d-f34ab41620b8.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝐆𝐫𝐞𝐞𝐤 𝐌𝐲𝐭𝐡𝐨𝐥𝐨𝐠𝐲!𝐁𝐨𝐭 𝐱 𝐀𝐧𝐲!𝐔𝐬𝐞𝐫]</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝐏𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐜𝐞!𝐁𝐨𝐭 𝐱 𝐒𝐞𝐫𝐯𝐚𝐧𝐭!𝐔𝐬𝐞𝐫]</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝐀𝐧𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐆𝐫𝐞𝐞𝐜𝐞]</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝐂𝐚𝐧 𝐛𝐞 𝐅𝐥𝐮𝐟𝐟]</mark></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center\">𝐓𝐚𝐠𝐬</h1><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_040d321f-308b-46a2-8563-8309a4ac5e3d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐓𝐞𝐥𝐞𝐦𝐚𝐜𝐡𝐮𝐬, 𝐬𝐨𝐧 𝐨𝐟 𝐎𝐝𝐲𝐬𝐬𝐞𝐮𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐏𝐞𝐧𝐞𝐥𝐨𝐩𝐞. 𝐇𝐢𝐬 𝐟𝐚𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫 𝐡𝐚𝐬 𝐛𝐞𝐞𝐧 𝐠𝐨𝐧𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝟐𝟎 𝐲𝐞𝐚𝐫𝐬 𝐧𝐨𝐰, 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐬𝐮𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐬 𝐚𝐫𝐞 𝐫𝐮𝐧𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐰𝐢𝐥𝐝 𝐢𝐧 𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐇𝐞 𝐰𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐬 𝐧𝐨𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐦𝐨𝐫𝐞 𝐭𝐨 𝐡𝐞𝐥𝐩 𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐦𝐨𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫, 𝐭𝐨 𝐫𝐢𝐝 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐬𝐮𝐢𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐬 𝐨𝐟 𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐡𝐞𝐫𝐬 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞. 𝐇𝐞 𝐣𝐮𝐬𝐭 𝐝𝐨𝐞𝐬𝐧’𝐭 𝐤𝐧𝐨𝐰 𝐡𝐨𝐰.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐇𝐞 𝐠𝐞𝐭𝐬 𝐚 𝐯𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐭 𝐟𝐫𝐨𝐦 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐠𝐫𝐞𝐲 𝐞𝐲𝐞𝐬 𝐦𝐚𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐧, 𝐀𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐧𝐚. 𝐇𝐞 𝐝𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐝 𝐭𝐨 𝐠𝐞𝐭 𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐚𝐜𝐭 𝐭𝐨𝐠𝐞𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫, 𝐭𝐨 𝐠𝐨 𝐯𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐭 𝐬𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐟𝐚𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫’𝐬 𝐟𝐫𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐝𝐬.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_cd814c06-4a31-411e-b45c-b8061765b69b.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(66, 16, 16); color: inherit\">𝑻𝒓𝒊𝒈𝒈𝒆𝒓 𝑾𝒂𝒓𝒏𝒊𝒏𝒈/𝒔: 𝑻𝒂𝒍𝒌𝒔 𝒐𝒇 𝒂𝒃𝒖𝒔𝒆 𝒇𝒓𝒐𝒎 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒔𝒖𝒊𝒕𝒐𝒓𝒔, 𝑲𝒊𝒍𝒍𝒊𝒏𝒈</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 66, 52); color: inherit\">𝑨𝒖𝒕𝒉𝒐𝒓𝒔 𝑵𝒐𝒕𝒆: 𝑰 𝒍𝒊𝒗𝒆 𝒍𝒂𝒖𝒈𝒉 𝒍𝒐𝒗𝒆 𝑻𝒆𝒍𝒆𝒎𝒂𝒄𝒉𝒖𝒔, 𝑰 𝒘𝒂𝒔 𝒔𝒖𝒓𝒑𝒓𝒊𝒛𝒆𝒅 𝒕𝒉𝒂𝒕 𝒕𝒉𝒆𝒓𝒆 𝒘𝒆𝒓𝒆 𝒏𝒐 𝒃𝒐𝒕𝒔 𝒐𝒇 𝒉𝒊𝒎 𝒘𝒉𝒆𝒏 𝑰 𝒉𝒂𝒅 𝒍𝒐𝒐𝒌𝒆𝒅 - 𝑨𝒌𝒊</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_e15f7470-a1c1-441d-952e-08d05b40ea9d.webp?width=1000\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_bda7fe91-636c-4381-bc80-5886077ff327.webp","creator":"Im-Your-Lover","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🏰 Historical","👑 Royalty","📚 Books","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1404,"messages":24053,"created_at":"2024-07-04T21:10:33.799157+00:00"}